description: Enumeration of all possible objects types that can be associated with a file.

enum.name: FileEntity
enum.description: A file in a folder or project.

enum.name: TableEntity
enum.description: A file in a table row.

enum.name: WikiAttachment
enum.description: A file attached to a wiki page.

enum.name: WikiMarkdown
enum.description: The file containing the markdown of a wiki page.

enum.name: UserProfileAttachment
enum.description: A file containing the user profile picture.

enum.name: MessageAttachment
enum.description: The file containing the content of a message.

enum.name: TeamAttachment
enum.description: A file containing the team icon.

enum.name: SubmissionAttachment
enum.description: A file attached to an evaluation submission.

enum.name: VerificationSubmission
enum.description: A file attached to a user verification submission.

enum.name: AccessRequirementAttachment
enum.description: A file included in an access requirement.

enum.name: DataAccessRequestAttachment
enum.description: A file attached to a data access request.

enum.name: DataAccessSubmissionAttachment
enum.description: A file attached to a data access submission.

enum.name: FormData
enum.description: A file containing the data of a form.
